<div class=" login-el  ">
  <!-- component -->
<div class="flex items-center  p-4  lg:justify-center mx-auto rounded-2xl my-5">
<div
class="flex flex-col-reverse overflow-hidden bg-cartColor rounded-md shadow-lg max md:flex-row md:flex-1 lg:max-w-screen-md"
>
<div
class="p-4 py-6 text-gray-900 bg-primaryColor md:w-80 md:flex-shrink-0 md:flex md:flex-col md:items-center md:justify-evenly"
>
<div class="my-3 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-wider text-center ">
  <a class="bg-cartColor pt-3  px-4 rounded-xl text-white" href="#">
    <span class="text-primaryColor text-4xl">JS</span>
    MAG.IR
  </a>
</div>
<p class="mt-6 font-normal text-center  md:mt-0">
  JSMAG بلاگ تخصصی آموزش Node.js  و تکنولوژی های سمت سروری جاوا اسکریپت
</p>
<p class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-10 text-center">
  <span>اکانت ندارید؟</span>
  <a href="/auth/signup" class="underline text-blue-600">ثبت نام</a>
</p>
<p class="mt-6 text-xs text-center ">
  کلیه حقوق محصولات و محتوای این سایت متعلق به JSMAG.IR می باشد و هر گونه کپی برداری از محتوا و محصولات سایت غیر مجاز و بدون رضایت ماست.  

</p>
</div>
<div class="p-5 bg-cartColor md:flex-1">
<h3 class="my-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Account Login</h3>
<form action="/auth/login" class="flex flex-col space-y-5" method="POST">
  <div class="flex flex-col space-y-1">
    <label for="email" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-200">آدرس ایمیل</label>
    <input
      name="email"
      type="email"
      id="email"
      autofocus
      class="px-4 py-2 transition duration-300 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:border-transparent focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-200"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col space-y-1">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
      <label for="password" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-200">پسورد</label>
      <a href="/auth/passwordRecovery" class="text-sm text-blue-400 hover:underline ">رمز خود را فراموش کرده اید؟</a>
    </div>
    <input
    name="password"
      type="password"
      id="password"
      class="px-4 py-2 transition duration-300 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:border-transparent focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-200"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
    <input
      type="checkbox"
      id="remember"
      class="w-4 h-4 transition duration-300 rounded focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-0 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-200 m-1"
    />
    <label for="remember" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-200">به خاطر سپردن</label>
  </div>
  <div>
    <button
      type="submit"
      class="w-full px-4 py-2 text-lg font-semibold text-white transition-colors duration-300 bg-blue-500 rounded-md shadow hover:bg-blue-600 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-200 focus:ring-4"
    >
      ورود
    </button>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col space-y-5">
    <span class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2">
      <span class="h-px bg-gray-400 w-14"></span>
      <span class="font-normal text-white">یا با گوگل وارد شوید</span>
      <span class="h-px bg-gray-400 w-14"></span>
    </span>
    <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4">
     
      <a
        href="<%= googleOAuthLogin %>"
        class="flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-2 space-x-2 transition-colors duration-300 border border-blue-500 rounded-md group hover:bg-blue-500 focus:outline-none"
      >
        <span>
          <svg class="text-blue-500 group-hover:text-white" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor">
            <path
              d="M6.29 18.251c7.547 0 11.675-6.253 11.675-11.675 0-.178 0-.355-.012-.53A8.348 8.348 0 0020 3.92a8.19 8.19 0 01-2.357.646 4.118 4.118 0 001.804-2.27 8.224 8.224 0 01-2.605.996 4.107 4.107 0 00-6.993 3.743 11.65 11.65 0 01-8.457-4.287 4.106 4.106 0 001.27 5.477A4.073 4.073 0 01.8 7.713v.052a4.105 4.105 0 003.292 4.022 4.095 4.095 0 01-1.853.07 4.108 4.108 0 003.834 2.85A8.233 8.233 0 010 16.407a11.616 11.616 0 006.29 1.84"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-blue-500 group-hover:text-white">Google</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</form>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

